Package: growkar
Title: Tidy Growth Curve Analysis for Optical Density Time Series
Version: 0.99.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Pooja", "Sethiya", 
           email = "pooja.sethiya@wimr.org.au", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools to import, tidy, visualize, summarize, and fit microbial
    growth curves from optical density time-series data. The package provides
    empirical estimation of growth rate and doubling time from observed data,
    exponential phase detection, and model-based fitting using logistic and
    Gompertz growth models.
